Posts.Content: Feb 8, 2012 09:43PM RhondaKennedy wrote: Try to stop jumping ahead, stage four seems to be doubtful, with what you posted, My breast Cancer was nearly the same, turns out My nodes were negative and everything was way better than I assumed, I know your scared (probably why your entire body hurts) I was just diagnosed on December 23, had double mastectomy on Jan 20, turns out that wasn't as bad a I thought either! Alot is good on this web site but until you have solid facts I may back off the internet for a bit (I just scared myself) I wish you well and I am sorry your dealing with this , if you have any questions feel free to write me, I work in health care as well....take care and you WILL get through this!!!! YOUR NOT GOING TO DIE! Just a curve in your life plan :) Rhonda
